00:26:34.580 --> 00:26:36.150 align:middle line:90%
of mass consciousness.

00:26:36.150 --> 00:26:37.550 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: Well, it's a very
significant documentary.

00:26:37.550 --> 00:26:37.850 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:26:37.850 --> 00:26:38.960 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: And the
reason being is

00:26:38.960 --> 00:26:41.126 align:middle line:84%
