00:26:52.270 --> 00:26:53.000 align:middle line:90%
>>STAVISH: About manipulation.

00:26:53.000 --> 00:26:54.064 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, exactly.

00:26:54.064 --> 00:26:55.730 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: The bias
I would say about it

00:26:55.730 --> 00:26:59.174 align:middle line:84%
