at what Bernays is saying,

00:27:10.040 --> 00:27:12.770 align:middle line:84%
prior to World
War I, advertising

00:27:12.770 --> 00:27:15.170 align:middle line:84%
had to do with selling
you a product based

00:27:15.170 --> 00:27:18.070 align:middle line:90%
on its utilitarian value.

00:27:18.070 --> 00:27:22.080 align:middle line:84%
Afterwards, it's based
upon pomp and appeal.

00:27:22.080 --> 00:27:22.880 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:27:22.880 --> 00:27:25.338 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: And then there's
even the manipulation of ideas.

00:27:25.338 --> 00:27:26.840 align:middle line:84%
How does he turn
cigarette smoking--

00:27:26.840 --> 00:27:28.131 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That was a brilliant.

00:27:28.131 --> 00:27:31.250 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: --into the early
women's liberation movement?

00:27:31.250 --> 00:27:33.740 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That is the
part that really struck

00:27:33.740 --> 00:27:39.830 align:middle line:84%
