00:27:52.250 --> 00:27:54.540 align:middle line:90%
it to us, so you must engage.

00:27:54.540 --> 00:27:55.505 align:middle line:90%
You know?

00:27:55.505 --> 00:27:57.630 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: Well, that's
the important word is sexy.

00:27:57.630 --> 00:27:57.770 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:27:57.770 --> 00:27:59.270 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: That's
the critical word.

00:27:59.270 --> 00:28:01.800 align:middle line:84%
Because if we look at the
book I just mentioned,

00:28:01.800 --> 00:28:10.370 align:middle line:84%
"Eros and Magic," eroticism,
the emotional appeal

00:28:10.370 --> 00:28:13.880 align:middle line:84%
of what we love, what
we're passionate about

00:28:13.880 --> 00:28:18.300 align:middle line:84%
starts first in terms
of human relationships.

00:28:18.300 --> 00:28:21.240 align:middle line:84%
So then we take that and
manipulate that and use that.

00:28:21.240 --> 00:28:27.080 align:middle line:84%
So when we look at all the
things in the news today, OK,

00:28:27.080 --> 00:28:30.260 align:middle line:84%
and I wrote something about
this last week sometime,

00:28:30.260 --> 00:28:33.380 align:middle line:84%
there's a reason why it
all focuses around sex

00:28:33.380 --> 00:28:35.630 align:middle line:90%
because it's unavoidable.

00:28:35.630 --> 00:28:38.820 align:middle line:84%
As much as we may want
to try, it's unavoidable.

00:28:38.820 --> 00:28:42.170 align:middle line:84%
So we use that as
the hook because that

00:28:42.170 --> 00:28:45.200 align:middle line:84%
is the beginning of the
pleasure principle in people.

00:28:45.200 --> 00:28:46.100 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:28:46.100 --> 00:28:48.950 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: So we all
want to feel good.

00:28:48.950 --> 00:28:49.820 align:middle line:90%
Buddhism says that.

00:28:49.820 --> 00:28:50.390 align:middle line:90%
What do we all want?

00:28:50.390 --> 00:28:51.440 align:middle line:90%
We all want to be happy.

00:28:51.440 --> 00:28:52.240 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:28:52.240 --> 00:28:53.090 align:middle line:90%
>>STAVISH: OK?

