OK, so we all want to feel good.

00:29:06.510 --> 00:29:07.310 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:29:07.310 --> 00:29:11.300 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: So if I can find
out two things, and Bruno talks

