OK, let's talk about
another differentiation

00:29:46.370 --> 00:29:50.732 align:middle line:84%
even within the Buddhist world,
the Tibetan tulpa versus tulku.

00:29:50.732 --> 00:29:52.940 align:middle line:10%
>>STAVISH: The reason I used
that example in the book

00:29:52.940 --> 00:29:55.190 align:middle line:10%
is because many of your
viewers are probably

00:29:55.190 --> 00:29:58.130 align:middle line:10%
