00:29:58.130 --> 00:29:59.885 align:middle line:10%
And if they're not,
they should be.

00:29:59.885 --> 00:30:01.510 align:middle line:10%
In particular, read
a biography on her.

00:30:01.510 --> 00:30:03.330 align:middle line:10%
She's just fantastic.

00:30:03.330 --> 00:30:05.060 align:middle line:10%
I mean, her life
story is just great.

00:30:05.060 --> 00:30:06.920 align:middle line:84%
And It ranks up
