OK?

00:35:08.430 --> 00:35:10.720 align:middle line:84%
The question is, are you
thinking carefully about yours?

00:35:10.720 --> 00:35:11.780 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, that's
what I'm asking.

00:35:11.780 --> 00:35:13.820 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: What is the
image you're presenting?

00:35:13.820 --> 00:35:16.820 align:middle line:84%
