00:36:18.920 --> 00:36:20.360 align:middle line:90%
each other's sentences.

00:36:20.360 --> 00:36:23.540 align:middle line:84%
But we have a freedom
that you didn't have.

00:36:23.540 --> 00:36:26.120 align:middle line:84%
We have a freedom to
