That's even better.

00:36:48.264 --> 00:36:50.180 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: And I don't
mean to nit pick there.

00:36:50.180 --> 00:36:50.660 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: No, no, no.

00:36:50.660 --> 00:36:50.840 align:middle line:90%
It's true.

00:36:50.840 --> 00:36:52.589 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: But to
