00:37:11.180 --> 00:37:17.390 align:middle line:84%
But as a group to have
been raised in this way,

00:37:17.390 --> 00:37:19.100 align:middle line:84%
I'm really concerned
about what is

00:37:19.100 --> 00:37:22.170 align:middle line:84%
the egregore that is going to
essentially whip them around

00:37:22.170 --> 00:37:22.970 align:middle line:90%
by its tail.

00:37:22.970 --> 00:37:25.310 align:middle line:84%
Because as you say,
egregores create

00:37:25.310 --> 00:37:27.740 align:middle line:84%
a, whether you call
yourself spiritual or not,

00:37:27.740 --> 00:37:31.607 align:middle line:90%
it is a spiritual slavery.

00:37:31.607 --> 00:37:32.940 align:middle line:90%
>>STAVISH: Well, that's the key.

00:37:32.940 --> 00:37:36.950 align:middle line:84%
And if you don't have
real freedom of choices,

00:37:36.950 --> 00:37:41.390 align:middle line:84%
if you don't have control over
your life, or at least more

00:37:41.390 --> 00:37:46.620 align:middle line:84%
control over your life and the
things that you do, then who

00:37:46.620 --> 00:37:47.930 align:middle line:90%
and what does?

