And when I look at, as you say,
the millennial generation--

00:37:51.394 --> 00:37:53.060 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Or younger,
way younger, yeah.

00:37:53.060 --> 00:37:56.730 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: --or younger, I'm not
