00:37:56.730 --> 00:37:57.530 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:37:57.530 --> 00:37:58.488 align:middle line:90%
That's what I'm seeing.

00:37:58.488 --> 00:38:01.180 align:middle line:84%
>>STAVISH: And that because
so much is being automated,

00:38:01.180 --> 00:38:04.920 align:middle line:84%
there's not even a process,
a reflection process.

00:38:04.920 --> 00:38:06.890 align:middle line:84%
So you have to
disengage, first of all,

00:38:06.890 --> 00:38:08.660 align:middle line:84%
