that, well, I'm saddled
by this, and I'm never

00:38:14.120 --> 00:38:17.590 align:middle line:84%
going to own a home, you've
made that choice now.

00:38:17.590 --> 00:38:19.250 align:middle line:90%
And I'm not saying it's easy.

