00:38:24.100 --> 00:38:26.300 align:middle line:90%
I know what this is like.

00:38:26.300 --> 00:38:29.240 align:middle line:84%
However, you still have
to then even be sharper

00:38:29.240 --> 00:38:31.010 align:middle line:90%
than the average tack.

00:38:31.010 --> 00:38:34.057 align:middle line:84%
You have to even step more
out of the collective.

00:38:34.057 --> 00:38:36.140 align:middle line:84%
Because what it is is what
